CSG_MEASURES.query:
--CSG LEADER PLUS 1

MasterHierarchy = load "Master_Hierarchy_GM";
MasterHierarchy = filter MasterHierarchy by'{{cell(Static_Cloud_Filter.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}'  in  {{cell(Static_Cloud_Filter.selection,0,"filter").asString()}};

-------------------LOAD ACV-------------------------------------
ACV = load "APM_ACV";
ACV = filter ACV by {{column(Filter_Lead.selection,["Lead"]).asEquality('Lead')}};
ACV = filter ACV by '{{cell(Static_Cloud_Filter.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}' in {{cell(Static_Cloud_Filter.selection,0,"filter").asString()}};

ACV = group ACV by ('{{cell(Static_Cloud_Filter.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}','{{cell(Static_Cloud_Filter.selection,0,"level_2").asString()}}', 'Quarter', 'Month', 'Fiscal_Year', 'Region', 'Country', 'Subcloud', 'Cloud_2');

ACV = foreach ACV generate '{{cell(Static_Cloud_Filter.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}' as '{{cell(Static_Cloud_Filter.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}', 
'{{cell(Static_Cloud_Filter.selection,0,"level_2").asString()}}' as '{{cell(Static_Cloud_Filter.selection,0,"level_2").asString()}}', 
'Quarter' as 'Quarter', 'Fiscal_Year' as 'Fiscal_Year' , 'Month' as 'Month', 'Region' as 'Region', 'Subcloud', 'Cloud_2', sum('ACV') as 'ACV',
{{cell(Static_Cloud_Filter.selection,0,"static_country_logic").asString()}} as 'Country'; 

ACV = filter ACV by {{column(lens_1.selection,["Country"]).asEquality('Country')}};

ACV_SuccessPlans = filter ACV by 'Subcloud' == "Success Plans";
ACV_SuccessPlans = filter ACV_SuccessPlans by {{column(Cloud_2_1.selection,["Cloud_2"]).asEquality('Cloud_2')}};

Advisory_Bookings = filter ACV by 'Subcloud' == "Advisory";
Advisory_Bookings = filter Advisory_Bookings by {{column(Cloud_2_1.selection,["Cloud_2"]).asEquality('Cloud_2')}};

Project_Bookings = filter ACV by 'Subcloud' == "Projects";
Project_Bookings = filter Project_Bookings by {{column(Cloud_2_1.selection,["Cloud_2"]).asEquality('Cloud_2')}};

----------------------------FILTER ACV--------------------------------------------
q2_CYACV = filter ACV_SuccessPlans by 'Month' in  {{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Month").asString()}}  && {{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"CY").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}};
q2_PYACV = filter ACV_SuccessPlans by 'Month' in  {{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Month").asString()}}  && {{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"PY").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}};
q3_CYACV = filter ACV_SuccessPlans by 'Month' in  {{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"YTD_Month").asString()}}  && {{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"CY").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}};
q3_PYACV = filter ACV_SuccessPlans by 'Month' in  {{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"YTD_Month").asString()}}  && {{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"PY").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}};

q2_CYACV_a = filter Advisory_Bookings by 'Month' in  {{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Month").asString()}}  && {{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"CY").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}};
q2_PYACV_a = filter Advisory_Bookings by 'Month' in  {{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Month").asString()}}  && {{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"PY").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}};
q3_CYACV_a = filter Advisory_Bookings by 'Month' in  {{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"YTD_Month").asString()}}  && {{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"CY").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}};
q3_PYACV_a = filter Advisory_Bookings by 'Month' in  {{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"YTD_Month").asString()}}  && {{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"PY").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}};

q2_CYACV_p = filter Project_Bookings by 'Month' in  {{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Month").asString()}}  && {{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"CY").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}};
q2_PYACV_p = filter Project_Bookings by 'Month' in  {{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Month").asString()}}  && {{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"PY").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}};
q3_CYACV_p = filter Project_Bookings by 'Month' in  {{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"YTD_Month").asString()}}  && {{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"CY").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}};
q3_PYACV_p = filter Project_Bookings by 'Month' in  {{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"YTD_Month").asString()}}  && {{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"PY").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}};


---------------------LOAD AOV----------------------------------------
AOV = load "APM_AOV";
AOV = filter AOV by '{{cell(Static_Cloud_Filter.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}' in {{cell(Static_Cloud_Filter.selection,0,"filter").asString()}};
AOV = filter AOV by {{column(Filter_Lead.selection,["Lead"]).asEquality('Lead')}};

--SPECIFIC FILTER FOR SUCCESS PLAN AOV
AOV = filter AOV by 'Subcloud' == "Success Plans";
AOV = filter AOV by {{column(Cloud_2_1.selection,["Cloud_2"]).asEquality('Cloud_2')}};

AOV = foreach AOV generate '{{cell(Static_Cloud_Filter.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}' as '{{cell(Static_Cloud_Filter.selection,0,"level_1").asString()}}', 
'{{cell(Static_Cloud_Filter.selection,0,"level_2").asString()}}' as '{{cell(Static_Cloud_Filter.selection,0,"level_2").asString()}}', 
'Quarter' as 'Quarter', 'Fiscal_Year' as 'Fiscal_Year','Month' as 'Month', 'Region' as 'Region', sum('AOV') as 'AOV',
{{cell(Static_Cloud_Filter.selection,0,"static_country_logic").asString()}} as 'Country';  

AOV = filter AOV by  {{column(lens_1.selection,["Country"]).asEquality('Country')}};

-----------------------------FILTER AOV ---------------------------------------
q2_CYAOV = filter AOV by 'Month' in {{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Month").asString()}}  && {{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"CY").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}};
q2_PYAOV = filter AOV by 'Month' in {{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Month").asString()}}  && {{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"PY").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}};
q3_CYAOV = filter AOV by 'Month' in {{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"YTD_Month_cum").asString()}} && {{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"CY").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}};
q3_PYAOV = filter AOV by 'Month' in {{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"YTD_Month_cum").asString()}} && {{cell(Fiscal_Year_1.selection,0,"PY").asEquality('Fiscal_Year')}};



--------------------------------------------------GROUPING LEVEL1-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

result = group 
q2_CYACV by 'Lead' full, 
q2_PYACV by 'Lead' full, 
q3_CYACV by 'Lead' full, 
q3_PYACV by 'Lead' full, 

q2_CYAOV by 'Lead' full, 
q2_PYAOV by 'Lead' full, 
q3_CYAOV by 'Lead' full, 
q3_PYAOV by 'Lead' full,  

q2_CYACV_a by 'Lead' full, 
q2_PYACV_a by 'Lead' full, 
q3_CYACV_a by 'Lead' full, 
q3_PYACV_a by 'Lead' full, 

q2_CYACV_p by 'Lead' full, 
q2_PYACV_p by 'Lead' full, 
q3_CYACV_p by 'Lead' full, 
q3_PYACV_p by 'Lead' full, 

MasterHierarchy by 'Lead';


-----------------PROJECTION LEVEL 1 ----------------------------------------------

result = foreach result generate 
"☁ " + coalesce(q2_CYACV.'Lead', q2_PYACV.'Lead', q3_CYACV.'Lead', q3_PYACV.'Lead', q2_CYAOV.'Lead', q2_PYAOV.'Lead', q3_CYAOV.'Lead', q3_PYAOV.'Lead', q2_CYACV_a.'Lead', q2_PYACV_a.'Lead', q3_CYACV_a.'Lead', q3_PYACV_a.'Lead', q2_CYACV_p.'Lead', q2_PYACV_p.'Lead', q3_CYACV_p.'Lead', q3_PYACV_p.'Lead') as 'Lead', 

" ☁ " + coalesce(q2_CYACV.'Lead', q2_PYACV.'Lead', q3_CYACV.'Lead', q3_PYACV.'Lead', q2_CYAOV.'Lead', q2_PYAOV.'Lead', q3_CYAOV.'Lead', q3_PYAOV.'Lead', q2_CYACV_a.'Lead', q2_PYACV_a.'Lead', q3_CYACV_a.'Lead', q3_PYACV_a.'Lead', q2_CYACV_p.'Lead', q2_PYACV_p.'Lead', q3_CYACV_p.'Lead', q3_PYACV_p.'Lead') as 'Lead_1', 

last(MasterHierarchy.'Lead_Rank') as 'Sort_Code',

coalesce(sum(q2_CYACV.'ACV'), 0) as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Success Plan ACV Absolute', 
coalesce(sum(q3_CYACV.'ACV'), 0) as 'YTD Success Plan ACV Absolute', 
((coalesce(sum(q2_CYACV.'ACV'), 0) - coalesce(sum(q2_PYACV.'ACV'), 0)) / coalesce(sum(q2_PYACV.'ACV'), 0)) * 100 as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_rate").asString()}} Success Plan ACV Growth', 
((coalesce(sum(q3_CYACV.'ACV'), 0) - coalesce(sum(q3_PYACV.'ACV'), 0)) / coalesce(sum(q3_PYACV.'ACV'), 0)) * 100 as 'YTD Success Plan ACV Growth', 

coalesce(sum(q2_CYAOV.'AOV'), 0) as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Success Plan AOV Absolute', 
coalesce(sum(q3_CYAOV.'AOV'), 0) as 'YTD Success Plan AOV Absolute', 
((coalesce(sum(q2_CYAOV.'AOV'), 0) - coalesce(sum(q2_PYAOV.'AOV'), 0)) / coalesce(sum(q2_PYAOV.'AOV'), 0)) * 100 as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_rate").asString()}} Success Plan AOV Growth', 
((coalesce(sum(q3_CYAOV.'AOV'), 0) - coalesce(sum(q3_PYAOV.'AOV'), 0)) / coalesce(sum(q3_PYAOV.'AOV'), 0)) * 100 as 'YTD Success Plan AOV Growth',

coalesce(sum(q2_CYACV_a.'ACV'), 0) as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Advisory ACV Absolute', 
coalesce(sum(q3_CYACV_a.'ACV'), 0) as 'YTD Advisory ACV Absolute', 
((coalesce(sum(q2_CYACV_a.'ACV'), 0) - coalesce(sum(q2_PYACV_a.'ACV'), 0)) / coalesce(sum(q2_PYACV_a.'ACV'), 0)) * 100 as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_rate").asString()}} Advisory ACV Growth', 
((coalesce(sum(q3_CYACV_a.'ACV'), 0) - coalesce(sum(q3_PYACV_a.'ACV'), 0)) / coalesce(sum(q3_PYACV_a.'ACV'), 0)) * 100 as 'YTD Advisory ACV Growth',

coalesce(sum(q2_CYACV_p.'ACV'), 0) as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Project ACV Absolute', 
coalesce(sum(q3_CYACV_p.'ACV'), 0) as 'YTD Project ACV Absolute', 
((coalesce(sum(q2_CYACV_p.'ACV'), 0) - coalesce(sum(q2_PYACV_p.'ACV'), 0)) / coalesce(sum(q2_PYACV_p.'ACV'), 0)) * 100 as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_rate").asString()}} Project ACV Growth', 
((coalesce(sum(q3_CYACV_p.'ACV'), 0) - coalesce(sum(q3_PYACV_p.'ACV'), 0)) / coalesce(sum(q3_PYACV_p.'ACV'), 0)) * 100 as 'YTD Project ACV Growth'
;

--------------------------GROUPING LEVEL2-----------------------------------------------

result_SubCloud = group 
q2_CYACV by ('Lead', 'Lead_1') full, 
q2_PYACV by ('Lead', 'Lead_1') full, 
q3_CYACV by ('Lead', 'Lead_1') full, 
q3_PYACV by ('Lead', 'Lead_1') full, 

q2_CYAOV by ('Lead', 'Lead_1') full, 
q2_PYAOV by ('Lead', 'Lead_1') full, 
q3_CYAOV by ('Lead', 'Lead_1') full, 
q3_PYAOV by ('Lead', 'Lead_1') full, 

q2_CYACV_a by ('Lead', 'Lead_1') full, 
q2_PYACV_a by ('Lead', 'Lead_1') full, 
q3_CYACV_a by ('Lead', 'Lead_1') full, 
q3_PYACV_a by ('Lead', 'Lead_1') full, 

q2_CYACV_p by ('Lead', 'Lead_1') full, 
q2_PYACV_p by ('Lead', 'Lead_1') full, 
q3_CYACV_p by ('Lead', 'Lead_1') full, 
q3_PYACV_p by ('Lead', 'Lead_1')
;


-------------------------------PROJECTION LEVEL2----------------------------------

result_SubCloud = foreach result_SubCloud generate 
"    ↳ " + coalesce(q2_CYACV.'Lead_1', q2_PYACV.'Lead_1', q3_CYACV.'Lead_1', q3_PYACV.'Lead_1', q2_CYAOV.'Lead_1', q2_PYAOV.'Lead_1', q3_CYAOV.'Lead_1', q3_PYAOV.'Lead_1', q2_CYACV_a.'Lead_1', q2_PYACV_a.'Lead_1', q3_CYACV_a.'Lead_1', q3_PYACV_a.'Lead_1', q2_CYACV_p.'Lead_1', q2_PYACV_p.'Lead_1', q3_CYACV_p.'Lead_1', q3_PYACV_p.'Lead_1') as 'Lead_1', 

"☁ " + coalesce(q2_CYACV.'Lead', q2_PYACV.'Lead', q3_CYACV.'Lead', q3_PYACV.'Lead', q2_CYAOV.'Lead', q2_PYAOV.'Lead', q3_CYAOV.'Lead', q3_PYAOV.'Lead', q2_CYACV_a.'Lead', q2_PYACV_a.'Lead', q3_CYACV_a.'Lead', q3_PYACV_a.'Lead', q2_CYACV_p.'Lead', q2_PYACV_p.'Lead', q3_CYACV_p.'Lead', q3_PYACV_p.'Lead') as 'Lead', 

coalesce(sum(q2_CYACV.'ACV'), 0) as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Success Plan ACV Absolute', 
coalesce(sum(q3_CYACV.'ACV'), 0) as 'YTD Success Plan ACV Absolute', 
((coalesce(sum(q2_CYACV.'ACV'), 0) - coalesce(sum(q2_PYACV.'ACV'), 0)) / coalesce(sum(q2_PYACV.'ACV'), 0)) * 100 as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_rate").asString()}} Success Plan ACV Growth', 
((coalesce(sum(q3_CYACV.'ACV'), 0) - coalesce(sum(q3_PYACV.'ACV'), 0)) / coalesce(sum(q3_PYACV.'ACV'), 0)) * 100 as 'YTD Success Plan ACV Growth', 

coalesce(sum(q2_CYAOV.'AOV'), 0) as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Success Plan AOV Absolute', 
coalesce(sum(q3_CYAOV.'AOV'), 0) as 'YTD Success Plan AOV Absolute', 
((coalesce(sum(q2_CYAOV.'AOV'), 0) - coalesce(sum(q2_PYAOV.'AOV'), 0)) / coalesce(sum(q2_PYAOV.'AOV'), 0)) * 100 as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_rate").asString()}} Success Plan AOV Growth', 
((coalesce(sum(q3_CYAOV.'AOV'), 0) - coalesce(sum(q3_PYAOV.'AOV'), 0)) / coalesce(sum(q3_PYAOV.'AOV'), 0)) * 100 as 'YTD Success Plan AOV Growth',

coalesce(sum(q2_CYACV_a.'ACV'), 0) as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Advisory ACV Absolute', 
coalesce(sum(q3_CYACV_a.'ACV'), 0) as 'YTD Advisory ACV Absolute', 
((coalesce(sum(q2_CYACV_a.'ACV'), 0) - coalesce(sum(q2_PYACV_a.'ACV'), 0)) / coalesce(sum(q2_PYACV_a.'ACV'), 0)) * 100 as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_rate").asString()}} Advisory ACV Growth', 
((coalesce(sum(q3_CYACV_a.'ACV'), 0) - coalesce(sum(q3_PYACV_a.'ACV'), 0)) / coalesce(sum(q3_PYACV_a.'ACV'), 0)) * 100 as 'YTD Advisory ACV Growth',

coalesce(sum(q2_CYACV_p.'ACV'), 0) as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Project ACV Absolute', 
coalesce(sum(q3_CYACV_p.'ACV'), 0) as 'YTD Project ACV Absolute', 
((coalesce(sum(q2_CYACV_p.'ACV'), 0) - coalesce(sum(q2_PYACV_p.'ACV'), 0)) / coalesce(sum(q2_PYACV_p.'ACV'), 0)) * 100 as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_rate").asString()}} Project ACV Growth', 
((coalesce(sum(q3_CYACV_p.'ACV'), 0) - coalesce(sum(q3_PYACV_p.'ACV'), 0)) / coalesce(sum(q3_PYACV_p.'ACV'), 0)) * 100 as 'YTD Project ACV Growth';


----------------------FINAL UNION-------------------------------

Final = union result, result_SubCloud;
Final = foreach Final generate 

'{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Success Plan ACV Absolute' as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Success Plan ACV Absolute', 
'YTD Success Plan ACV Absolute' as 'YTD Success Plan ACV Absolute', 
'{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_rate").asString()}} Success Plan ACV Growth' as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Success Plan ACV Growth', 
'YTD Success Plan ACV Growth' as 'YTD Success Plan ACV Growth', 

'{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Success Plan AOV Absolute' as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Success Plan AOV Absolute',
'YTD Success Plan AOV Absolute' as 'YTD Success Plan AOV Absolute', 
'{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_rate").asString()}} Success Plan AOV Growth' as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Success Plan AOV Growth', 
'YTD Success Plan AOV Growth' as 'YTD Success Plan AOV Growth',

'{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Advisory ACV Absolute' as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Advisory ACV Absolute', 
'YTD Advisory ACV Absolute' as 'YTD Advisory ACV Absolute', 
'{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_rate").asString()}} Advisory ACV Growth' as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Advisory ACV Growth', 
'YTD Advisory ACV Growth' as 'YTD Advisory ACV Growth',

'{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Project ACV Absolute' as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Project ACV Absolute', 
'YTD Project ACV Absolute' as 'YTD Project ACV Absolute', 
'{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_rate").asString()}} Project ACV Growth' as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Project ACV Growth', 
'YTD Project ACV Growth' as 'YTD Project ACV Growth',

'Lead' as 'Lead', 
'Lead_1' as 'Lead_1', 
case when ('Lead' == "☁ Tony Owens") then "1. Tony Owens" 
when ('Lead' == "☁ Warren Wick") then "2. Warren Wick"  
when ('Lead' == "☁ Andrew Kofoid") then "3. Andrew Kofoid" 
when ('Lead' == "☁ Miguel Milano") then "4. Miguel Milano" 
when ('Lead' == "☁ Mark Innes") then "5. Mark Innes" 
when ('Lead' == "☁ Shinichi Koide") then "6. Shinichi Koide" 
when ('Lead' == "☁ Dave Rey") then "7. Dave Rey" 
when ('Lead' == "☁ Enrique Ortegon") then "8. Enrique Ortegon" 
when ('Lead' == "☁ Other") then "9. Other" else "10. unkown" end as 'Lead_Rank',

case when('Lead_1' == "    ↳ Other") then "    ↳ Z.Other" else 'Lead_1' end as 'Lead_1_Rank'

;


--------------------------ORDERING LEAD RANK------------------
Final = order Final by ('Lead_Rank' asc, 'Lead_1_Rank' asc);

------------------IMPLEMENT FAKE NONE FOR UNION ----------------------------------------------------------

None = foreach Final generate 
0 as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Success Plan ACV Absolute', 
0 as 'YTD Success Plan ACV Absolute', 
0 as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Success Plan ACV Growth', 
0 as 'YTD Success Plan ACV Growth', 

0 as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Success Plan AOV Absolute',
0 as 'YTD Success Plan AOV Absolute', 
0 as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Success Plan AOV Growth', 
0 as 'YTD Success Plan AOV Growth',

0 as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Advisory ACV Absolute', 
0 as 'YTD Advisory ACV Absolute', 
0 as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Advisory ACV Growth', 
0 as 'YTD Advisory ACV Growth',

0 as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Project ACV Absolute', 
0 as 'YTD Project ACV Absolute', 
0 as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Project ACV Growth', 
0 as 'YTD Project ACV Growth',
"None" as 'Lead', 
"None" as 'Lead_1',
"None" as 'Lead_Rank';

----------------------------FINAL UNION--------------------------------

Result = union Final, None;
Result = filter Result by 'Lead' != "None";
Result = filter Result by 'Lead_1' != "    ↳ N/A";

Result = foreach Result generate 
'Lead_1'+"                  " as 'Lead_1', 
'{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Success Plan ACV Absolute' as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Success Plan ACV Absolute', 
'YTD Success Plan ACV Absolute' as 'YTD Success Plan ACV Absolute', 
'{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Success Plan ACV Growth' as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Success Plan ACV Growth', 
'YTD Success Plan ACV Growth' as 'YTD Success Plan ACV Growth', 

'{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Success Plan AOV Absolute' as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Success Plan AOV Absolute',
'YTD Success Plan AOV Absolute' as 'YTD Success Plan AOV Absolute', 
'{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Success Plan AOV Growth' as '{{cell(Selector_Quarter.selection,0,"Header_name_absolute").asString()}} Success Plan AOV Growth',

parameters.text:
** DATA WILL BE UPDATED AS A PART OF THE REGULAR REFRESH BY MID MAY **
$10M+ Deals: Deals at the global company level with ACV value >= $10M
$1M+ deals: Deals at the global company level with ACV value >= $1M (inclusive of the above)
Run Rate Volume: Count of deals at global company level below a specific ACV threshold (i.e., high transaction volume) dependent on region and segment.
For example, AMER Run Rate thresholds: ENTR >$500k, CMRCL >$50K, ESMB >$5K, USPS >$50K
New Logos: Customer crosses the AOV threshold (beg AOV + ACV): ESMB: $0, CMRCL: $10K, EBU: $50K
Lost Logos: When a customer AOV goes to decreases to $0 and is not clawed back

Within the AE, Co Prime, SE sections, % columns 3 & 4 represent 24 month CAGR (quarterly and YTD)
AEs: Includes ECS, Marketing Cloud (Messaging/Journies), and Commerce Cloud AE's
SEs: Excludes Q Branch, Spark, IPD, and SE Management
Co Prime: CSG Coprime = APs (account partners) that worked through the Qtr
